Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:40.93,sign_3564_24_A_Mad_Hand_Appea,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Mad Hand\NAppeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.10,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat fans like the Mad Hands in DQ!
