Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.78,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get flushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.40,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the large option will flush your \Nevil deeds and Clift's feelings away!
