Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.76,Main,Tae,0000,0000,0000,,The moment we get the fans \Ninside, we've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:57.67,Main,Tae,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the money will flow in even \Nif the movie's a steady stream of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.10,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the outrageous statements!
