Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:18.18,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm lining up for Otae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.09,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,She seems prim and proper, but is \Nactually really bold! She's the best!
