Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.19,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since a line's formed, \Nlet's just go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.44,Main,Sac,0000,0000,0000,,Pfft! Don't make me laugh!
