Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.00,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.78,Main,Sac,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else be center.
