Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:18:00.54,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,please don't come to hate Terakado Tsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.29,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend me your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.05,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow members who have walked with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.80,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,fans who have cheered me on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.76,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,and rivals who have competed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.81,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,All of you have been my pillar of support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:26.27,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You are all part of Booger Diamonds 48, \Nand I dedicate this song to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.81,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}An Idol's Badge of Honor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:34.69,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, idol
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:40.53,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, idol
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:46.29,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Accel, consul, it's dreams that we sell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.32,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Idol, idol, idling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:55.01,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Even on the edge, we've got the handling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:06.60,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,That scandal back then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:12.36,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Was a summer sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:17.24,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's do or die, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:23.12,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,I could end up doing pillow business
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:28.92,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Even that day of the month is safe and secure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:38.47,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet, blood ruby, an idol's badge of honor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:44.35,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, idol
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:49.69,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, idol
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:55.36,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Foot soldier, loot and plunder, pillow seller
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.44,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Idol, idol, idling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:03.70,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,We can't swerve around aging
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.20,sign_28705_341_Oedo_Dome,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(567,1)}Oedo Dome
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.96,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic it is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.52,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,that the stage on which an idol \Nstands to give people dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.24,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,is built on the wrecks of \Ncountless other dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:26.01,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why she shines brightly, \Nlike a lone star in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.23,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,She will walk over our dreams \Nand those of her friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.61,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,and continue down this path \Nof chaos we call idol stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:39.78,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you'll be able to \Nmake up for what you've sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:44.12,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,You just let go of a talent \Nthat could surpass Otsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.55,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,She has the ruthlessness \Nto take down her enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.58,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,and the selflessness to cast \Nherself aside to help her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:56.42,Main,Bit,0000,0000,0000,,A diamond covered in boogers,\Nwith two totally contrasting faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gin-san, Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:00.37,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait a second. Aren't you gonna watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:01.62,Main,OMom,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I asked her if she \Nwould like to keep at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.89,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn it, I couldn't make any money again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.43,Main,OMom,0000,0000,0000,,but she refused, saying she was \Nalready part of an idol group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.18,Main,OMom,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad, but she's fine that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.18,Main,OMom,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she shines brightest \Nin that group of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.61,Main,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond all the cigarettes, \Nalcohol, and shaved heads,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.45,Main,Song,0000,0000,0000,,the one who filled me \Nwith passion again was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:31.68,Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, you, you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.08,Main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thenk you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:10.80,Song,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off already
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:13.78,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Otsu-chan really is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:16.77,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something off about her lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:20.77,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what she started doing, \Neven though she's an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:25.13,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was influenced by \Nan idol group she really loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:29.41,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,A group that disbanded right \Nafter making its debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.70,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What was it called, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:33.15,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Booger Diamonds 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.21,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The phantom idol \Ngroup, Booger Diamonds 48!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:42.21,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,It's no phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.71,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,It remains in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:48.26,Main,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,as the idol group of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:57.35,sign_34163_377_Preview,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.47,Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Just to let you know in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:57.98,Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,this isn't a sales promotion \Nfor our upcoming game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:24:00.85,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,1)}The Line Between Godlike Games and Shitty Games Is Paper-Thin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.53,Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We're just messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:06.23,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:06.23,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,so keep that in mind, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:12.28,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we're again \Ngoing with wave, wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:12.28,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,and standing all the way!
